{"tid":1860591,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[仆街啦]  深圳市最多確診病例的是鄰近深圳灣口岸的南山區　","createTime":"2020-02-03T17:40:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T09:38:31.000Z","uid":141151,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c6fc87e93ff5f0fb86959c7a00b43e81d501e13a","tid":1860591,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:40:43.000Z","msg":"深圳市最多確診病例的是鄰近深圳灣口岸的南山區　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506442-20200203.htm?fbclid=IwAR0qCsWyasbOf_wtm4_5J-Ch--fUEhM_CcFR-7CE0fRcq8PebU2vqQ2UYes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506442-20200203.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0qCsWyasbOf_wtm4_5J-Ch--fUEhM_CcFR-7CE0fRcq8PebU2vqQ2UYes&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=1dca0ef6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506442-20200203.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0qCsWyasbOf_wtm4_5J-Ch--fUEhM_CcFR-7CE0fRcq8PebU2vqQ2UYes&h=b4957701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506442-20200203.htm?fbclid=IwAR0qCsWyasbOf_wtm4_5J-Ch--fUEhM_CcFR-7CE0fRcq8PebU2vqQ2UYes</a><br />\n<br />\n深圳市今日新增19宗新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎病例，累計確診245宗。全市最多病例是鄰近深圳灣口岸的南山區，有50宗。<br />\n<br />\n其次是福田區，有45宗；龍崗區有38宗；羅湖區有17宗。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市衞健委公布，245宗確診病例中，危重病例有5宗，重症病例有24宗。<br />\n<br />\n香港特區政府宣布午夜起關閉4個口岸，包括羅湖、落馬洲支線、皇崗及港澳碼頭，並不包括深圳灣口岸。根據入境處數據，深圳灣是昨日最多內地旅客入境的陸路口岸，有2253人次。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔怪得之唔封深圳灣</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0411cac6b25570529728caccff1c4c1957933987","tid":1860591,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:46:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b516133fb26b1c3384192f56d6700de96cd998fd","tid":1860591,"uid":282280,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:48:38.000Z","msg":"林鄭一定要凌遲"},{"pid":"a0c517adda2192bde35409addcced3000c1f0e14","tid":1860591,"uid":92353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6fc87e93ff5f0fb86959c7a00b43e81d501e13a","tid":1860591,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T17:40:43.000Z","msg":"深圳市最多確診病例的是鄰近深圳灣口岸的南山區　<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506442-20200203.htm?fbclid=IwAR0qCsWyasbOf_wtm4_5J-Ch--fUEhM_CcFR-7CE0fRcq8PebU2vqQ2UYes\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506442-20200203.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0qCsWyasbOf_wtm4_5J-Ch--fUEhM_CcFR-7CE0fRcq8PebU2vqQ2UYes&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdM0oCCb%2BFWW1Qd8KXu5iEc8%3D&h=1dca0ef6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506442-20200203.htm%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0qCsWyasbOf_wtm4_5J-Ch--fUEhM_CcFR-7CE0fRcq8PebU2vqQ2UYes&h=b4957701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506442-20200203.htm?fbclid=IwAR0qCsWyasbOf_wtm4_5J-Ch--fUEhM_CcFR-7CE0fRcq8PebU2vqQ2UYes</a><br />\n<br />\n深圳市今日新增19宗新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎病例，累計確診245宗。全市最多病例是鄰近深圳灣口岸的南山區，有50宗。<br />\n<br />\n其次是福田區，有45宗；龍崗區有38宗；羅湖區有17宗。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市衞健委公布，245宗確診病例中，危重病例有5宗，重症病例有24宗。<br />\n<br />\n香港特區政府宣布午夜起關閉4個口岸，包括羅湖、落馬洲支線、皇崗及港澳碼頭，並不包括深圳灣口岸。根據入境處數據，深圳灣是昨日最多內地旅客入境的陸路口岸，有2253人次。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔怪得之唔封深圳灣</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"rep